background_description: The expansive sky is dominated by heavy, dark grey storm clouds with distinct undulating, wave-like, and mammatus-like formations, showing variations in tone from very dark to lighter grey and some brighter patches where light penetrates. Below, the landscape includes a two-lane road, grassy embankments, and a series of low-rise commercial or industrial buildings with light brown/pink walls, dark flat roofs, and evenly spaced rectangular windows. Streetlights and sparse trees are also visible.
